data.description: Home, sweet home! This fantastic 3 bed, 2 bath residence now on the market is looking for its new owners! A beautiful facade w/stone accents, easy-care front yard, a 2 car garage w/built-in cabinets, and an RV gate are just the beginning! Inside you'll find a spacious dining & living area w/elegant wood-look flooring, dazzling light fixtures, upgraded ceiling fans, custom palette throughout, outdoor access w/stylish French doors, and a warm fireplace. The gorgeous kitchen is comprised of wood cabinetry w/granite counters, a pantry, stainless steel appliances, stone backsplash, and a lovely island. Discover a cozy loft where you can spend a relaxing Sunday evening! The primary bedroom boasts vaulted ceilings, private balcony access, a walk-in closet, and a full ensuite w/dual sinks. Also including a wonderful backyard w/a covered patio, a quaint pergola, and a sparkling blue pool, this home simply has it all! Act now before it's gone!
